{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":7,"isBulletin":116},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6},"Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento","Caminneci, Parello, Soraci","2023","\u003Cspan>Valentina Caminneci, Maria Concetta Parello, e Cristina Soraci, «Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento», in \u003Ci>Indagini archeologiche nell’insula IV del Quartiere Ellenistico Romano di Agrigento, 2014-2018\u003C/i>, a c. di Valentina Caminneci et al. (L’Aquila: One Group Edizioni, 2023), 537–49\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/A7HRWIUH",[8],{"file":9,"uri":9,"title":10,"status":11,"editionAuthor":13,"type":14,"objectType":18,"material":22,"condition":28,"layoutDesc":29,"handNote":36,"date":50,"places":55,"geo":65,"country":60,"provenance":57,"provenanceGeo":69,"region":72,"settlement":62,"repository":73,"idno":77,"textLang":79,"tmNumber":28,"facsimile":83,"letterHeights":89,"publications":94,"zotero":96,"keywords":98,"html":108,"bibl":109,"bulletinDateSort":115,"citedRangeSort":110,"languageSort":80,"materialSort":23,"typeSort":15},"ISic001830","Building inscription of Martinianos",{"_":12},"draft",null,{"_":15,"ana":16,"ref":17},"building","#function.building","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},"plaque","#object.plaque","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259",{"_":23,"ana":24,"type":25,"subtype":26,"ref":27},"marble","#material.inorganic.stone.metamorphic_rock.marble","stone.marble","unverified","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html","",{"layout":30},{"p":31,"rs":32,"damage":28},"Traces of three lines of ancient Greek are preserved, with guidelines above and below; upper, left and right margins are partially preserved. The text appears to maintain a consistent margin on the left, but not on the right.",{"_":33,"ana":34,"ref":35},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":37,"dimensions":38},"Tall, regular, narrow letters, v-cut, with small serifs on the termination of strokes. Small deep triangular interpuncts. Alpha has broken bar; epsilon tall, narrow, with equal short horizontals; theta and omicron are rhomboid; mu has vertical first and last, with the diagonals starting below the top and only desencing to the mid-point; nu is similar; rho has small curved, closed loop; sigma is lunate but rectilinear, with very short horizontals.",[39,46],{"type":40,"l":41,"from":42,"to":43,"h":44,"unit":45,"atLeast":44,"atMost":44},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","110","mm",{"type":47,"l":48,"from":42,"to":43,"h":49,"unit":45,"atLeast":49,"atMost":49},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","20",{"_":51,"notBefore":52,"notAfter":53,"evidence":54},"Dated by reference to Flavius Martinianos, consularis of Sicily between 352 and 358 CE (Soraci)",352,358,"prosopography",[56,61],{"_":57,"type":58,"ref":59,"region":60},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086","Sicilia",{"_":62,"type":63,"ref":64,"region":60},"Agrigento","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[66],[67,68],37.32084,13.58876,[70,71],37.297649,13.591579,"Sicily",{"_":74,"role":75,"ref":76},"Parco Archeologico Valle dei Templi","site","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/200",{"type":78},"inventory",{"_":80,"mainLang":81,"languages":82},"Ancient Greek","grc",[80],{"n":84,"url":85,"height":86,"width":87,"desc":28,"surfaceType":88},"screen","ISic001830_tiled.tif","5520px","3680px","front",[90,92],{"atLeast":91,"atMost":91},110,{"atLeast":93,"atMost":93},20,[95],"Caminneci, Parello, Soraci, 2023, Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",[97],"A7HRWIUH",[99,100,101,15,19,23,102,103,104,105,103,106,107,81],"isic001830","building inscription of martinianos",{"_":12},"agrigentum","agrigento","sicilia","sicily","parco archeologico valle dei templi","ancient greek